{"tid":2479450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍67歲生日感謝全世界影迷祝福 同成家班傾新戲當做慶祝活動","createTime":"2021-04-07T22:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T22:45:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2acc13ef9b7b778a23e80bcb1ffb061a8437c20","tid":2479450,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T22:41:54.000Z","msg":"早前成龍出席中美合作的動畫《Wish Dragon》記者會，被目睹步履蹣跚需要兩個人扶着走路，今日他留言表示早段時間自己的腰傷復發，但現時身體狀況已無大礙，可以全情投入拍攝工作，朋友和影迷可以放心。<br />\n<br />\n其實成龍近年的票房號召力每況愈下，他參演的電影《急先鋒》去年10月在大陸上映時，票房包尾不特止，還被網民鬧爆劇情老套無聊。不過鬧還鬧，成龍生日依然照開工，果然活到老，做到老，但最緊要好好保護條腰。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210407/3T35ZIKVZBGHTLSI7HQ574YZWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210407%2F3T35ZIKVZBGHTLSI7HQ574YZWE%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=4e192f14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210407%2F3T35ZIKVZBGHTLSI7HQ574YZWE%2F&h=b0613c1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210407/3T35ZIKVZBGHTLSI7HQ574YZWE/</a>"},{"pid":"5dd2fb0abeecdf7dadc413e6be167ef57f2cc0e5","tid":2479450,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T22:45:16.000Z","msg":"前幾個鐘twitter仲見到jackie chan trending<br />\n點都上去賀賀佢<br />\n比外國人睇吓呢隻共狗真面目<br />\n其實佢係過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asiatimes.com/2020/06/movie-star-jackie-chan-backs-new-hk-security-law/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasiatimes.com%2F2020%2F06%2Fmovie-star-jackie-chan-backs-new-hk-security-law%2F&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYfQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=b49eaa8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asiatimes.com/2020/06/movie-star-jackie-chan-backs-new-hk-security-law/</a>"}]}